// NumberInput
// Numeric input with increment and decrement buttons, min/max clamping.

FUNCTION clamp(value, min, max) -> number
  Returns the value constrained to the [min, max] range.

---

FUNCTION handleChange(e)
  Parses the raw input string as a number.
  Clamps to min/max bounds.
  Calls onChange with the clamped value.

---

FUNCTION handleStep(direction)
  Increments or decrements the value by the step amount.
  Clamps result to min/max bounds.
  Calls onChange with the new value.

---

FUNCTION NumberInput(props) -> ReactNode                                  EXPORT
  Renders a text input flanked by decrement (−) and increment (+) buttons.
  Validates and clamps on change.
  Disables the decrement button at min and the increment button at max.
